OL,6,FA man who was banned from approaching
OL,7,Fhis sister after a string of
OL,8,Fconfrontations hacked her to death
OL,9,Fwith a Samurai sword in the street, a
OL,10,Fcourt heard.
OL,12,FRoger Harriott 56, waited for mother-
OL,13,Fof-two Sandra Harriott to leave the
OL,14,Fhome she shared with their elderly
OL,15,Fmother in before attacking her on 26
OL,16,FMay last year.
OL,18,FIn an incident caught on CCTV he used
OL,19,Fa 55cm sword to inflict numerous
OL,20,Finjuries on her.
