OL,4,CSamurai sword jailed for life
OL,6,FShe died in hospital.
OL,8,FLeeds Crown Court heard Harriott was
OL,9,Fthe subject of a non-molestation order
OL,10,Fbanning him from going to her home on
OL,11,FRipon Avenue or contacting her.
OL,13,FIt followed a series of incidents in
OL,14,Fwhich he abused his sister, drove at
OL,15,Fher with his car and hit a wall with a
OL,16,Fmachete.
OL,18,FHe was also accused of exploiting his
OL,19,Fmother's finances ` a claim he denied.
