OL,6,FProsecutor David Hall said CCTV
OL,7,Ffootage showed Sandra Harriott leaving
OL,8,Fher home and opening the boot of her
OL,9,Fcar.
OL,11,FHarriott left his car holding a
OL,12,FSamurai sword and ran towards her,
OL,13,Fwhile she attempted to flee.JHe struck
OL,14,Fher in the face, causing her to fall
OL,15,Fto the floor, before slashing her
OL,16,Fseven further times.
