OL,6,FMr Hall added: "He then uses the sword
OL,7,Fforcibly to stab her twice to the
OL,8,Fbody. She can be seen writhing on the
OL,9,Fground and kicking out to defend
OL,10,Fherself. He turns towards his car
OL,11,Fbefore turning back and stabbing her
OL,12,Fonce more in the chest with his sword.
OL,13,FShe then ceases moving. It was only
OL,14,Fthen he turns and leaves."
