OL,6,FHarriott later went to a police
OL,7,Fstation and said: "I've just killed
OL,8,Fsomeone, can you open the door and
OL,9,Fcome and arrest me please...."JHe then
OL,10,Fdirected police to the sword in the
OL,11,Ffront of his car, which was found with
OL,12,Fblood on it.
OL,14,FThe attack took place just eight days
OL,15,Fafter
OL,17,FHarriott admitted murder.
