OL,3,CMan who hacked sister to death with
OL,4,CSamurai sword jailed for life
OL,6,FJailing him for 23 years, Judge Robin
OL,7,FMairs told him his sister's life "was
OL,8,Fended by you in a brutal, vicious and
OL,9,Fmerciless attack outside her home."JHe
OL,10,Fsaid: "You were lying in wait for your
OL,11,Fsister to appear. The murder was
OL,12,Fcaptured on CCTV. That footage is
OL,13,Fchilling."JThe judge said just weeks
OL,14,Fbefore the murder, in an interview,
OL,15,FHarriott described his relationship
OL,16,Fwith his sister as "toxic." Judge
OL,17,FMairs said the murder was
OL,18,F"foreshadowed by a litany of abuse and
OL,19,Fthreats."JHe added: "It was committed
OL,20,Fin broad daylight, in a public street.
OL,21,FThe attack was callous and determined."
